# Cursor Rules for Naik Kelas 2.0

> **Primary reference**: See `AGENTS.md` and `CLAUDE.md` at the project root for comprehensive coding guidelines, architecture, and design system documentation.

## Quick Rules

- **Framework**: SvelteKit 2 + Svelte 5 Runes (`$props()`, `$state()`, `$derived()`)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4 — use `bg-linear-to-*` not `bg-gradient-to-*`
- **Design**: Import tokens from `$lib/config/design` — never hardcode colors or shadows
- **Props**: Use `$props()` with TypeScript interfaces — never use `export let`
- **Validation**: Run `pnpm run check` after every change — must pass with 0 errors/warnings
- **Server**: Never import `$lib/server/*` in client `.svelte` files
- **HTML**: Always close elements explicitly (Svelte 5 warns on implicit closing)
- **Responses**: The user prefers responses in Indonesian (Bahasa Indonesia)

## Design Tokens

```ts
import { COLOR, TEXT, RADIUS, ELEVATION, TRANSITION, SPACING, GRADIENT } from '$lib/config/design';
```

## Key Files

- `src/lib/config/design.ts` — All design tokens
- `src/lib/server/rbac.ts` — Role-based navigation & permissions
- `src/lib/server/db/schema.ts` — 44 Drizzle tables
- `src/lib/components/layouts/` — AppShell, Sidebar, DashboardHeader
- `AGENTS.md` — Full AI agent coding guidelines
- `CLAUDE.md` — Detailed architecture & patterns reference
